# SkillSpark AI — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your real values
# NEVER commit .env — only commit .env.example

# Primary LLM (judges use one of these)
CLAUDE_API_KEY=your_claude_api_key_here

# Free alternative for testing
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Server
BACKEND_PORT=8000
FRONTEND_PORT=3000
ENVIRONMENT=development
APP_NAME=SkillSpark-AI
```

---

### The rule is simple
```
.env.example   → COMMIT ✓   (template, no real values)
.env           → NEVER  ✗   (real API keys, in .gitignore)